Swing version 0.01
==================

Java::Swing is a Perl module providing Java Swing bindings.  To use
it you need to have Inline and Inline::Java installed, but you code solely
in Perl.  This is similar to kits like Perl/Tk and Gtk2::.

SEE ALSO

For further information on using Java::Swing, see GUIDE in the distribution.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Inline
  Inline::Java

